---
import { getWhatsappUrl } from "src/utils/whatsapp";
---

<section class="hero-section text-white pt-28 pb-20 md:pt-40 md:pb-32">
	<div class="px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-0 max-w-[820px] mx-auto text-center">
		<h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
			Confianza, calidad y transparencia <span class="text-dark-orange">en cada operación</span>
		</h1>
		<p class="text-sm md:text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
			En Eiich Inmobiliaria, creemos que una buena experiencia inmobiliaria se basa en la confianza, la
			transparencia y un trato profesional.
		</p>
		<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center px-6">
			<a
				href="#values"
				class="bg-dark-orange hover:bg-[#e6732b] text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold transition transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center"
			>
				<i class="fas fa-star mr-2"></i> Nuestros valores
			</a>
			<a
				href={getWhatsappUrl()}
				target="_blank"
				rel="noopener noreferrer"
				class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white hover:bg-white hover:text-midnight-blue text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold transition transform hover:scale-105 flex items-center justify-center"
			>
				<i class="fas fa-phone mr-2"></i> Contáctanos
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.hero-section {
		background: linear-gradient(rgba(12, 38, 71, 0.8), rgba(12, 38, 71, 0.8)),
			url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600585154340-be6161a56a0c?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1470&q=80");
		background-size: cover;
		background-position: center;
	}
</style>
